        //re-bind shareThis links
        $kj('#shareThisModal').on('show.bs.modal', function (event) {
            var button = $kj(event.relatedTarget);
            var itemLink = button.data('link');
            var itemTitle = button.data('title');

            var modal = $kj(this);
            modal.find('.modal-body span').remove();
            var shareThisParams = "";
            if (typeof itemLink != 'undefined' && typeof itemTitle != 'undefined') {
                shareThisParams = "st_url='" + itemLink + "' st_title='" + itemTitle + "'";
            }
            modal.find('.modal-body').append("<span class='st_sharethis_large' st_via='' " + shareThisParams + "></span>");
            modal.find('.modal-body').append("<span class='st_facebook_large' st_via='' " + shareThisParams + "></span>");
            modal.find('.modal-body').append("<span class='st_twitter_large' st_via='' " + shareThisParams + "></span>");
            modal.find('.modal-body').append("<span class='st_instagram_large' st_via='' " + shareThisParams + "></span>");
            modal.find('.modal-body').append("<span class='st_linkedin_large' st_via='' " + shareThisParams + "></span>");
            modal.find('.modal-body').append("<span class='st_plusone_large' st_via='' " + shareThisParams + "></span>");
            modal.find('.modal-body').append("<span class='st_email_large' st_via='' " + shareThisParams + "></span>");

            if (window.stButtons) {
                stButtons.locateElements();
            }
        });
        $kj('#shareThisModal').on('hide.bs.modal', function (event) {
            var modal = $kj(this);
            modal.find('.modal-body span').removeAttr("st_url");
            modal.find('.modal-body span').removeAttr("st_title");
            modal.find('.modal-body span').removeAttr("st_processed");
        });

    }

</script>
